OL,3,CMan coerced boy, 15, into delivering
OL,4,Cdrugs by buying him expensive gifts
OL,6,FA man from has been given a Slavery
OL,7,FTrafficking Risk Order after a court
OL,8,Fheard how he was using a child to run
OL,9,Fdrugs for him around the town.
OL,11,FThe man befriended a 15-year-old boy
OL,12,Fin March 2022 and then started to buy
OL,13,Fthe teenage boy expensive gifts, which
OL,14,Fwere used to encourage him to run
OL,15,Fdrugs around Telford.
OL,17,FThe man in his 20s, who cannot be
OL,18,Fnamed for legal reasons, was given the
OL,19,Forder by Telford Magistrates'
OL,20,Fyesterday (Monday 18 March).
