OL,6,FHe was given a three-year Slavery
OL,7,FTrafficking Risk Order, which is the
OL,8,Ffirst West Mercia Police has handed
OL,9,Fout that gives restrictions around
OL,10,Funder 18s.
OL,12,FThe order means the man must not
OL,13,Ffacilitate travel for anyone who is
OL,14,Funder the age of 18 unless they are
OL,15,Fpart of his immediate family.
OL,17,FIt also restricts his use of devices
OL,18,Fthat have internet access.
