OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Louise Hickman,
OL,7,Ffrom Telford's Child Exploitation
OL,8,FTeam, said:
OL,10,F"This is the first order of its kind
OL,11,Fthat the force has had granted against
OL,12,Fa child, and I believe given the
OL,13,Fnature of the modern slavery the
OL,14,Fteenager was exposed to, that it was
OL,15,Fthe right decision made by the
OL,16,Fmagistrates.
