OL,6,F"The defendant will now be managed by
OL,7,Fthe Child Exploitation Team at West
OL,8,FMercia, who will visit him unannounced
OL,9,Fon a regular basis, and manage the
OL,10,Frisk by ensuring he is complying with
OL,11,Fthe order handed to him in court.
OL,13,F"We would urge anyone with any
OL,14,Fconcerns about modern slavery to
OL,15,Fplease get in touch. We act on all
OL,16,Freports we receive and offer full
OL,17,Fsupport to anyone who feels they are a
OL,18,Fvictim of this type of crime."
